'''新南门站'''位于[[成都市|成都市]][[武侯区|武侯区]]新南路与致民路交叉口，车站沿新南路南北方向布置<ref name="封顶">{{cite news | title = 成都地铁三号线3站封顶 首现地下三层车站 | publisher = 网易 | date = 2013-05-03 | url = http://news.163.com/13/0503/03/8TTUUFOE00014AED.html | accessdate = 2013-05-03 | language = zh | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170831172222/http://news.163.com/13/0503/03/8TTUUFOE00014AED.html | archive-date = 2017-08-31 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，是[[成都地铁3号线|成都地铁3号线]]的地下[[岛式站台|岛式车站]]，于2016年7月31日启用<ref name="启用">{{cite news  | title = 成都地铁3号线一期工程试运营 熊猫主题列车首发  | publisher = 新浪  | date = 2016-07-31  | url = http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2016-07-31/doc-ifxunuyk4220798.shtml  | accessdate = 2016-07-31  | language = zh  | archive-date = 2016-08-01  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160801212833/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2016-07-31/doc-ifxunuyk4220798.shtml  | dead-url = no  }}</ref>。本站得名于1939年成都市在老城区南侧上莲池街和下莲池街附近的老城墙上开凿的新城门——复兴门，又称新南门。因临近复兴桥，车站以“水润成都”、“天作之合”为主题<ref>{{cite news | title = 成都地铁3号线一期车站亮相 高升桥站再现三国故事(组图) | publisher = 网易 | date = 2016-06-07 | url = http://news.163.com/16/0607/10/BOV12VMP00014AEE.html | accessdate = 2016-06-07 | language = zh | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170803045307/http://news.163.com/16/0607/10/BOV12VMP00014AEE.html | archive-date = 2017-08-03 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。在建设过程中的工程名为“滨江路站”<ref>{{cite news | title = 成都地铁3号线6站点月底开工 2015年成都地铁网建成 | publisher = 四川在线 | date = 2012-04-20 | url = http://sichuan.scol.com.cn/cddt/content/2012-04/20/content_3643515.htm | accessdate = 2012-04-20 | language = zh | archive-date = 2017-08-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170816110700/http://sichuan.scol.com.cn/cddt/content/2012-04/20/content_3643515.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。
